               <t:floruit notBefore="1832" notAfter="1855">He was the nominal ruler of <t:placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC3010Ethiop">Ethiopia</t:placeName> alternately in the 1840s and 1850s with
               <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10377Yohanne">Yoḥannǝs III</t:persName>. He was involved in establishing and endowing the monastery of
               <t:placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC2552Darasg">Darasge Māryām</t:placeName>.</t:floruit>
            </t:person>
